data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom twinhome in West Fargo, ND! This home has everything you need and more, including an open floorplan, and a large backyard. The main level features a bright and airy living room with vaulted ceilings. The lower level family room is perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing with your family. The home also has an attached two-stall garage for your convenience. If you're looking for a move-in ready home in West Fargo, this twinhome is the perfect choice for you! Schedule your showing today and see for yourself why this home is so special. This wont last long!
